title: Episode 201: Lip Service Live Part 2 (Feat. Trina)
itunes:title: Episode 201: Lip Service Live Part 2 (Feat. Trina)
description:
Thank you so much to Trina for joining the ladies of Lip Service in the second half of the live show! The ladies cover topics such as training their men to please them how they like, dealing with sneaky men, and much more. Trina even ranks her exes on a scale of 1-10...enjoy!
